  ('00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000043', '10000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000007', $f$What is the trustee office administration fee?$f$, $f$Trustee centers charge for processing DLD appointments and paperwork bundles. It is separate from DLD transfer fee.

