  ('00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000044', '10000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000007', $f$Are there penalties for late registration of tenancy?$f$, $f$Ejari and municipal rules may impose fines or block certain services if registration lags. Compliance protects both parties.

