  ('00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000046', '10000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000007', $f$What hidden costs surprise first-time UAE buyers?$f$, $f$Mortgage arrangement fees, valuation fees, life insurance premiums, moving and fit-out, and short-term rent overlap add up.

