  ('00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000047', '10000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000008', $f$Is Dubai Marina still a strong rental market?$f$, $f$Marina remains liquid with international tenant demand, though yields compress when prices rise. View, tower quality, and parking drive spreads.

