  ('00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000048', '10000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000008', $f$What defines Palm Jumeirah premium pricing?$f$, $f$Frond versus trunk positioning, private pool, beach access, and hotel branding all matter. Maintenance and service levels are high.

