  ('00000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000049', '10000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000008', $f$Are Downtown Dubai yields lower than outer communities?$f$, $f$Prime central locations often trade yield for liquidity and brand. Compare net income after service charges.

