  ('00000000-0000-4000-8000-00000000004a', '10000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000008', $f$Is Arabian Ranches suited for family buyers?$f$, $f$Low-rise villas with schools and community facilities appeal to long-tenure families. Commute patterns matter.

