  ('00000000-0000-4000-8000-00000000004c', '10000000-0000-4000-8000-000000000008', $f$How should I compare JVC versus JVT?$f$, $f$Both offer dense mid-rise stock at accessible price points; build quality, parking, and traffic patterns differ by cluster.

